{"tid":1381582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［和理非+勇武入］ 全民戴口罩運動","createTime":"2019-07-29T09:22:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T09:46:51.000Z","uid":143151,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d34beef6b4ad8eaba318d2181ddfd3f8c6e36046","tid":1381582,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:22:29.000Z","msg":"前排有人戴頭盔出街 希望俾國際睇到香港唔安全<br />\n可惜接力嘅人唔多<br />\n<br />\n如果用口罩 會唔會方便大家出手<br />\n好似日本人咁 每日都戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n首先 唔會有人覺得奇怪 因為本身就係良好衞生意識<br />\n第二 香港人咁重視私隱 戴住個口罩緊係安心啲<br />\n第三 口罩依家有咁多功能 保濕美顏防塵 總有一款幫到你<br />\n第四 和理非定勇武派 蓮登到child 登到做得<br />\n第五 方便使用 翻工搭車行街都戴得 唔想戴又可以即除<br />\n<br />\n唔想膠化件事 <br />\n認真討論下 大家會唔會有興趣實行<br />\n低成本 又做到互相支持效果<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">約定大家 聽日一齊戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hb3MrgO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHb3MrgO.png&h=7004e381&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c897e21b359cfb9360bb665690df772e428a0a32","tid":1381582,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:26:30.000Z","msg":"我深信有日 大家可以一齊除口罩 輕輕鬆鬆食餐飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"76823696a1eb2b37912b78301516a7b83206042f","tid":1381582,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:28:02.000Z","msg":"同埋好多人一發完夢 係狗鐵站已經除口罩<br />\n俾啲衛生意識好冇！！！！！！！"},{"pid":"c7f3488a1bd19962d40813358c85e17adf10dad4","tid":1381582,"uid":143151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T09:29:03.000Z","msg":"推！！！！！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr